node.text:
With this year being both the 25th anniversary of Pokémon and the fifth anniversary of Pokémon GO, this year’s Pokémon GO Fest is sure to be a special event! #PokemonGOFest2021

Join us as we go behind the scenes with some Niantics who were there when Pokémon GO launched, and learn what it was like when Pokémon GO changed the world in 2016.
Check out this and other #PokemonGOFest2021-themed video and audio content here: https://pokemongolive.com/post/pokemongofest2021-content

node.text: Thank you to every single Trainer who joined us in exploring the world in search of Pokémon! We’re glad to have made some amazing friends and memories along the way. Here’s to you, Trainers! Happy #PokemonGO5YearAnniversary!

node.text: So, several days ago we posted a video about fellow Trainer, Jessica, seeking some help on how to get better at raiding. Fast forward to today, we’re happy to share how far she’s come thanks to your help and the tips shared by the Pokémon GO community! #TogetherWeRaid

node.text: ICYMI: Team GO Rocket took over Day 2 of #PokemonGOFest2020 around the world. To hold back their take-over efforts, Team Leaders Spark, Blanche, and Candela faceoff in a battle between #TeamGORocket Leaders Sierra, Cliff, and Arlo!

node.title: Pokémon GO Fest 2020: Team GO Rocket face-off

node.text: Good news, Trainers! Buddy Adventure has completed rolling out! It is now live for Trainers level 2 and above. Have fun on your future #PokemonGOBuddy adventures!

node.title: NOW LIVE: Pokémon GO Buddy Adventure!

node.text:
Whether you’re a veteran Trainer or just starting your journey with Pokémon GO, everybody has that special Pokémon buddy. 🤩 We’re excited to announce that Trainers and their Buddy Pokémon will soon have more ways to connect, interact, and explore the world.

It’s time for another adventure, Trainers. A #PokemonGOBuddy Adventure. 🤩

Learn more by visiting the link in our bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 29, 2021. May be a cartoon of outdoors and text.

node.text: Zamazenta in its Hero of Many Battles form will be appearing in five-star raids during the upcoming Bonus Raid Hour on Monday, August 30, 2021, from 6 p.m. to 7 p.m. local time.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 27, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text.

node.text: The Season of Mischief begins in just a few days! 🤪 There’ll also be plenty more to look forward to coming in the month of September. https://pokemongolive.com/post/sept-2021-events

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 27, 2021. May be an image of outdoors and text.

node.text:
Get ready for the Season of Mischief! This Season will focus on Hoopa, the Mischief Pokémon, which you’ll be able to encounter during this Season’s Special Research story! 😜 https://pokemongolive.com/post/season-of-mischief-2021

Let us know what you think of the new blog design!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 26, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text:
🥊 GO Battle League Season 9 is on the way! 🥊

You can look forward to a new cup, new avatar items, strong Pokémon to encounter, and lots of opportunities to collect Stardust!

For more details, visit https://pokemongolive.com/post/gobattleleague-season9. 

Let us know what you think of the new blog design!

#GOBattle

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 26, 2021. May be a cartoon of 1 person and text.

node.text:
🥚 Egg check-in! 🥚

Trainers, which of these Pokémon originally discovered  in the Galar region have you hatched from Eggs today?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 26, 2021. May be a cartoon of 2 people and text.

node.text:
🥊 GO Battle Night is happening tonight! 🥊

From 6:00 p.m. to 11:59 p.m. local time, you’ll be able to enjoy a 3× Stardust bonus and a total of 20 battle sets!

More details here: https://pokemongolive.com/post/gobattleleague-season8

#GOBattle

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 25, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: As you look for even more Pokémon originally discovered in the Galar region, remember to record your findings by taking a #GOsnapshot of some of your favorite encounters. This might be a limited-time event, but memories are forever!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 25, 2021. May be a cartoon of text.

node.text: Known as the Warrior Pokémon, Zacian absorbs metal particles, transforming them into a weapon it uses to battle. ⚔️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 24, 2021. May be an anime-style image.

node.text: Remember, Trainers! Different Pokémon will be available to challenge in raids at different times during the Ultra Unlock Part 3: Sword and Shield event! Learn more: https://pokemongolive.com/post/pokemongofest2021-ultraunlock-sword-shield

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 23, 2021. May be an anime-style image of 4 people, people standing and text.

node.text: Uniforms that appear in the Galar region are now available as avatar items in Pokémon GO! Pick up the Gym Challenger Uniform avatar item for free, which is worn by Pokémon Trainers challenging Gyms in the Galar region.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 23, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'POKéMON 5ÄNNIVERSARY to Aug 20 10:00 a.m. LOCALTIME LOCAL Aug 26 10:00 a.m. LOCALTIME TIME to Aug 26 10:00 a.m. LOCAL TIME Sept 1 10:00 a.m. LOCAL TIME'.

node.text: Remember to continue growing your Friends list, Trainers—you’ll need all the help you can get when challenging Mega Raids! The following Mega-Evolved Pokémon will be appearing in Mega Raids throughout August!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Pokémon GO on August 22, 2021. May be an image of outdoors.

node.text: Did you know? Wooloo’s curly fleece is such an effective cushion that this Pokémon could fall off a cliff and stand right back up at the bottom, unharmed.
